Paper Submission:
-----------------
Papers must be submitted electronically via the CORCS 2011 Submission 
Page (http://rs-1.cs.iastate.edu/CORCS2011/). The format of submitted 
papers should follow the guidelines for the IEEE conference proceedings. 
All papers will be carefully reviewed by at least three reviewers. 
Papers should be no more than 6 pages. Accepted papers will be published 
by the IEEE Computer Society Press.

